name: Hat
descriptionHtml: The Next.js beanie has arrived! This embroidered beauty has a snug fit that ensures you're going to feel cozy and warm whatever you're doing.

name: Mask
descriptionHtml: This durable face mask is made from two layers of treated fabric and features elastic ear loops and a center flat seam that ensure a close fit. It's machine-washable and reusable. Sold in packs of 3.

name: Short sleeve t-shirt
descriptionHtml: A super-soft, form-fitting, breathable t-shirt with a slightly lower neckline than a classic t-shirt.

name: Lightweight Jacket
descriptionHtml: Add a little zing to your winter wardrobe with this vibrant Winter-breaker Jacket. Black hardware.
